These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, epic, family, fantasy, mystery, western
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, january, june, april, september, november, december
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 9. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
10. the person watching family movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person watching family movies is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person watching epic movies##2
12. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | family | epic  | fantasy | crime | disaster | western |
| Birthday           | june | january   | december | april  | november   | september    | october    |

