.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey, ebony, purple, brown, white, pink
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes grey##2
 9. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
11. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | milk   | almond-milk | soy-milk | 7up     | lemonade |
| Color   | grey     | fuchsia  | brown | white     | pink  | ebony | purple |

