There 7 different types of food: garlic, strawberry, pumpkin, orange, blueberry, cranberry, pomegranate
 1. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 9. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4   |     5     |       6       |    7    |
| Beverage      | 7up       | cola     | lemonade | juice | milk      | hot-chocolate | sprite  |
| Food   | garlic | cranberry | pumpkin   | strawberry | orange | pomegranate       | blueberry |

