.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-6::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: green, apricot, fuchsia, red, blue, ivory, purple
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, electronic, folk, funk, indie, pop, rock
 1. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 2. the fan of funk is the person who likes red##1
 3. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 4. the fan of indie is the person who likes purple##1
 5. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
 6. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 7. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the fan of pop is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
11. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
12. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
13. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
14. the person who likes blue is on the right of the fan of folk##1
15. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Color   | green | blue    | apricot | ivory   | purple | red | fuchsia |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | electronic | rock     | classical | indie     | funk   | pop     |

