10. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
11. the fan of pop is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama         | family | epic   | crime        | superhero  | romance  | horror |
| Music-Genre         | trance | electronic  | jazz | folk | indie | house | pop |

