.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate, tea, iced-tea, juice
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, horror, mystery, scientific, thriller
 1. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |    5    |      6       |      7      |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | fanta   | tea | mirinda    | soy-milk   | juice | iced-tea     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | action | horror        | adventure | mystery | scientific   | documentary |

 